overview: Steve is the Director of the Kevin and Debra Rollins Center for eBusiness and is also a Professor of Information Systems at the Marriott School of Management. Holder of a Ph.D. in Computer Science, he is an expert in information architecture, web development, practical application of computer systems, conceptual modeling, and e-business. Steve has actively developed software and consulted for major clients such as Intel, ACS, and U.S. Bancorp for more than two decades.
